  "detailed_description": "I_Darkness is a puzzle game in an escape room scenario created by one person using Unreal Engine 4.<br />\r\nPuzzles are designed to test the player's general knowledge and riddle solving skills.<br />\r\nExplore the beautiful mansion with its many rooms and corridors. <br />\r\nLearn how difficult it is to leave the house when darkness surrounds you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Investigate and learn how to activate mechanisms to unlock access to further content<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Solve puzzles and collect items required to finish the game",
